# k8s/
#
# This directory will hold Kubernetes manifests for the personal-assistant application:
#   - Deployment        (backend pod spec, replicas, resource limits)
#   - Service           (ClusterIP for internal traffic)
#   - Ingress           (Traefik IngressRoute or standard Ingress for TLS termination)
#   - PersistentVolumeClaim  (if local storage is needed alongside the DB)
#
# Manifests are applied via ArgoCD (see infra/argocd/).
